features: GLOWS IN THE DARK: Contains one night pacifiers for baby that glows in the dark, making it easy for you to locate quickly at night without any stumbling and searching, so your baby can sleep better.
ANTI SLIP SILICONE NIPPLE: The BPA-free silicone boy and girl pacifier has the signature MAM design, with silky SkinSoft material and a symmetrical shape that's ideal for jaw and teeth development.
VENTILATED & COMFORTABLE SHIELD: These cute pacifiers for babies have a curved sterilizing shield with openings to keep baby comfortable, prevent moisture build-up, and allow baby’s skin to breathe.
SYMMETRICAL DESIGN: The 6+ months breastfeed pacifier for babies is fun and functional. The curved shield with wide openings are always right-side up and prevent skin irritation with maximum airflow.
HIGH QUALITY: Approved by 94% of babies*, our 100% BPA & BPS free orthodontic silicone pacifiers meet or exceed US safety standards and are extremely durable, while being soft and flexible.
body.description: This variety breastfeed pacifier pack includes two cute daytime pacifiers, one air version and one original, as well as one of our glow in the dark pacifier, making it easy for baby and parent to find in the dark. BPA/BPS-free MAM Pacifiers were developed by leading pediatric dentists and developmental psychologists to provide maximum comfort and style for babies 6 months of age and older*. These orthodontic pacifiers for baby include a built-in air channel that naturally flattens and extends when sucked, mimicking a human nipple during breastfeeding, plus symmetrical nipple that fits perfectly in baby’s mouth at any angle. MAM pacifiers all feature life-like, SkinSoft textured silicone that feels just like mom. The MAM Air pacifier in this collection has a shield that is specially designed for babies with sensitive skin. The extra wide air holes allow plenty of circulation around your baby's mouth and even allow you to peek at their little smile. MAM nipples are easily accepted by babies of all ages, with 94% nipple acceptance among babies tested.** *Developed in conjunction with the International Children’s Medical Research Society. ***Market research 2010-2020, tested with 1,572 babies

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 16, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Obsessed baby. Happy mama.
reviews.reviewText: These are the only pacifiers my 10 month old will take. He loves them. He hides them in his toybox & bedroom. He somehow shows up with them in his mouth when he’s in his playpen or his bedroom. The glow in the dark feature is AMAZING. He finds these no problems at night when he wakes him and puts himself right back to sleep, with non glowing pacifiers that doesn’t usually happen. Also it makes them easier to find when he throws them out of his crib. I can’t recommend these enough for picky babies!
